<section>
<h2>Maintaining Brand Consistency</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0">BCG uses the TED@BCG event to curate their thought leadership on particular topics. The focus of 2016 was their perspective on growing businesses in a rapidly changing world.</p>

<h5>The video had to:</h5>
<ol>
  <li>Feel similar to its sister video</li>
  <li>Use the existing design elements</li>
  <li>End on the Onwards & Upwards title lockup</li>
</ol>
</section>

