<h3>The Approach</h3>
</div>

<div class="white-bg">
<section>
<h2>Blending nature and industry</h2>
<p>BCG's writings covered a diverse range of topics, but they all emphasized the connection between business growth and growth in nature. Three core principles of growth manifested:</p>

<p class="emph">Growth is natural.</p>

<p class="emph left">Growth is constant motion.</p>

<p class="emph">Growth is omnipresent.</p>

<p>These core ideas informed all of our decisions going forward. From the footage choices to the every detail of the motion, <b>everything needed to have flow.</b></p>
</section>
</div>


